# GitHub Linguist: only Rust sources count toward the language bar.
# This avoids the repo being labeled “Makefile” / TOML when lockfiles or other files outweigh src/.
* linguist-vendored
*.rs linguist-vendored=false

*.md linguist-documentation
Cargo.lock linguist-generated
target/** linguist-vendored

# If a Makefile exists on the default branch, don’t let it define the repo language
Makefile linguist-vendored
makefile linguist-vendored
GNUmakefile linguist-vendored
